WEBVTT

00:08:30.400 --> 00:08:34.096
The idea was to allow them
to reach their desired destination,

00:08:34.120 --> 00:08:35.760
if only after their death.

00:08:36.960 --> 00:08:39.976
Such acts of beautification
may not be pretty,

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:41.256
but they are much needed.

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:44.736
Because things tend to get ugly
when there's only one meaning, one truth,

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:46.200
only answers and no questions.

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:49.880
Beautiful organizations
keep asking questions.

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:52.600
They remain incomplete,

00:08:53.275 --> 00:08:55.656
which is the fourth
and the last of the principles.

00:08:55.680 --> 00:08:57.216
[Remain Incomplete]

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.560
Recently I was in Paris,

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:02.376
and a friend of mine
took me to Nuit Debout,